headline: PG&E Invites Customers to a Webinar on Wildfire Prevention Work and Safety Resources for 2025
summary: Pacific Gas and Electric Company (PG&E) invites customers to an interactive webinar to share more about what we are doing to reduce wildfire risk and make our system safer.
